rows.label: qev012103_MSG0002
rows.name:
Heh heh. What can I say? I owe you for
about a million and one things.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012103_MSG0003
rows.name:
I'd have been dead a dozen times over by now
if not for you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012103_MSG0004
rows.name: And this time was especially bad...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012103_MSG0005
rows.name:
One of those painful reminders of how big
and scary the world can be.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012103_MSG0007
rows.name:
I guess I have to admit that charging into danger on
my own like this is crazy. So maybe it's time...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012103_MSG0008
rows.name:
Time that I got better gear! That's it, all right!
I'd be fine right now if I'd been equipped like
a champ instead of a chump.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012103_MSG0009
rows.name: Other than that, I don't think I did anything wrong.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012103_MSG0010
rows.name:
Yep, yep, yep. Definitely need to stock up
before my next adventure.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012103_MSG0011
rows.name: Which means I'm gonna need some cash.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012103_MSG0013
rows.name:
Dad always said sponsors are an explorer's
best friend...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012103_MSG0016
rows.name: Oh! Sorry, Chief. You still here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012103_MSG0017
rows.name:
Aw, don't worry about me. I'll be fine.
You go knock those missions dead![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012103_MSG0018
rows.name:
If I've got anything going for me, it's resilience!
...And my good looks. But mostly resilience.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012103_MSG0019
rows.name: Thanks so much for checking in on me![ST:wait ]
